'''John D. Payne''', or '''J. D. Payne''', is an American screenwriter and producer. Alongside [[Patrick McKay]], he is the "showrunner"<ref>[https://www.facebook.com/LOTRonPrime/videos/401382077176163/ "Meet our Fellowship" Video] at The Lord of the Rings on Prime Facebook page, 7/28/19</ref> of the entire series, ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power‎]]''.

